Subject: [PATCH] gh-146211: Reject CR/LF in HTTP tunnel request headers
 (GH-146212) (cherry picked from commit
 05ed7ce7ae9e17c23a04085b2539fe6d6d3cef69)

Co-authored-by: Seth Larson <seth@python.org>
